{
  "analytics_identifier": null,
  "base_path": "/check-your-driver-cpc-periodic-training-hours",
  "content_id": "3b2792dc-69a4-4b60-8abe-92657c8e7c55",
  "description": "Check how many hours of Driver CPC periodic training you’ve done and which courses you’ve attended.",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>Use this service to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>check how many hours of Driver Certificate of Professional Competence (<abbr title=\"Certificate of Professional Competence\">CPC</abbr>)  training you’ve done</li>\n  <li>check which courses you’ve attended</li>\n  <li>check when you’ll get your next Driver <abbr title=\"Certificate of Professional Competence\">CPC</abbr> card</li>\n  <li>create a temporary password for your employer so they can view your record</li>\n  <li>view your employee’s record if they’ve given you a temporary password</li>\n</ul>\n\n",
    "more_information": "<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://driver-services.dvsa.gov.uk/cpcode/flow/user?register=yes\">Register to use the service</a> if you’re a new user.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You cannot register until the training centre has recorded your first Driver CPC training course. </p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You’ll need your:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>driving licence number</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>home postcode</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>A password will be sent by post to the address on your driving licence. </p>\n\n<p>If you do not receive your password letter within 3 working days and you live in England, Scotland or Wales, contact <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>DVSA Driver CPC<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:cpcre@dvsa.gov.uk\">cpcre@dvsa.gov.uk</a><br>\nTelephone: 0300 123 7721<br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 5pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>If you live in Northern Ireland, contact <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Agency\">DVA</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>DVA Driver CPC<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:CPC.Enquiries@infrastructure-ni.gov.uk\">CPC.Enquiries@infrastructure-ni.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"problems-with-your-record\">Problems with your record</h2>\n\n<p>Contact the training centre if any training you’ve done is not showing on your record after 5 working days.  </p>\n\n<p>If the training centre has stopped trading and they have not updated your training record, you can <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.citizensadvice.org.uk/consumer/somethings-gone-wrong-with-a-purchase/if-a-company-stops-trading-or-goes-out-of-business/\">get help from Citizens Advice</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"if-you-need-help-using-this-service\">If you need help using this service</h2>\n\n<p>If you live in England, Scotland or Wales, contact <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>DVSA Driver CPC<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:cpcre@dvsa.gov.uk\">cpcre@dvsa.gov.uk</a><br>\nTelephone: 0300 123 7721<br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 5pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>If you live in Northern Ireland, contact <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Agency\">DVA</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>DVA Driver CPC<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:CPC.Enquiries@infrastructure-ni.gov.uk\">CPC.Enquiries@infrastructure-ni.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
